{"id": 3069, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你的看剧习惯和偏好都发生了哪些变化？", "description": "跟之前相比，这几年你的追剧生活出现了啥新动向？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 8205, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201911242339539bUMsPDQBdwVtOCg.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-24T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6066, "title": "现如今你的看剧习惯和偏好都发生了哪些变化？", "content": "现如今你的看剧习惯/偏好都发生了哪些变化？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349723, "content": "不怎么通过电视机看剧，而是转移到了视频网站上", "image": "img/option/option/20191124221137iL0jBwPrIfvxaWZd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349724, "content": "基本都是 1.5 或者 2 倍速看（已然离不开进度条了", "image": "img/option/option/20191124221454Gf7rc5Jogpi1uytK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349725, "content": "对比较虐的情节耐受度降低，更爱看所谓的甜剧/爽剧", "image": "img/option/option/20191124221905evgs2BbAYjS74GKw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349726, "content": "“冲着某个片段入坑”的剧很多，但追完并反复看的很少", "image": "img/option/option/20191124222824Ie1WktmEMwGU3YHg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349727, "content": "习惯性参考评分网站，看剧前必须先看打分/剧评", "image": "img/option/option/20191124223046k8bo4zuUDlQ2yxhc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349728, "content": "可选范围极大丰富，完全不看国产剧也没问题", "image": "img/option/option/201911242233388pd1QzU3ubriPZHx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349729, "content": "由“播啥看啥”变成“探索出一整套避雷方法论”", "image": "img/option/option/201911242253529boIL862dHC1qkOK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349731, "content": "很快进入“种草一堆神剧然而积压着没空看”的阶段", "image": "img/option/option/201911242237143Kz4Nqs9FMXhCjZV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349730, "content": "可选的娱乐越来越多，“看剧”这件事占比越来越小", "image": "img/option/option/20191124223814IA1hxaKXEo504gZj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349732, "content": "都不是，我倒是有别的发现", "image": "img/option/option/20191124224037gAWt4xYGXT7ukM3U.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}